description: Trillion Energy International Inc. operates as an oil and gas exploration and production company with assets in Turkey and Bulgaria. It owns 49% interests in the SASB natural gas field; 19.6% ownership interest in the Cendere oil field; 50% operating interest in the shut-in Bakuk gas field located near the Syrian border; and the Vranino 1-11 block, a 98,205 acres oil and gas exploration land located in Dobrudja Basin, Bulgaria. The company was formerly known as Park Place Energy Inc. and changed its name to Trillion Energy International Inc. in April 2019. Trillion Energy International Inc. was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
